title: Rebecca
overview: A self-conscious woman juggles adjusting to her new role as an aristocrat's wife and avoiding being intimidated by his first wife's spectral presence.

title: Trois couleurs: Rouge
overview: A model discovers a retired judge is keen on invading people's privacy.

title: Hable con ella
overview: Two men share an odd friendship while they care for two women who are both in deep comas.

title: Un long dimanche de fiançailles
overview: Tells the story of a young woman's relentless search for her fiancé, who has disappeared from the trenches of the Somme during World War One.

title: El secreto de sus ojos
overview: A retired legal counselor writes a novel hoping to find closure for one of his past unresolved homicide cases and for his unreciprocated love with his superior - both of which still haunt him decades later.

title: Moon
overview: Astronaut Sam Bell has a quintessentially personal encounter toward the end of his three-year stint on the Moon, where he, working alongside his computer, GERTY, sends back to Earth parcels of a resource that has helped diminish our planet's power problems.

title: Titanic
overview: A seventeen-year-old aristocrat falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.

title: Gegen die Wand
overview: With the intention to break free from the strict familial restrictions, a suicidal young woman sets up a marriage of convenience with a forty-year-old addict, an act that will lead to an outburst of envious love.

title: Gilda
overview: A small-time gambler hired to work in a Buenos Aires casino discovers his employer's new wife is his former lover.

title: Casablanca
overview: A cynical expatriate American cafe owner struggles to decide whether or not to help his former lover and her fugitive husband escape the Nazis in French Morocco.

title: Laura
overview: A police detective falls in love with the woman whose murder he is investigating.

title: Mulholland Dr.
overview: After a car wreck on the winding Mulholland Drive renders a woman amnesiac, she and a perky Hollywood-hopeful search for clues and answers across Los Angeles in a twisting venture beyond dreams and reality.

title: Brief Encounter
overview: Meeting a stranger in a railway station, a woman is tempted to cheat on her husband.

title: Dev.D
overview: After breaking up with his childhood sweetheart, a young man finds solace in drugs. Meanwhile, a teenage girl is caught in the world of prostitution. Will they be destroyed, or will they find redemption?

title: Before Sunset
overview: Nine years after Jesse and Celine first met, they encounter each other again on the French leg of Jesse's book tour.

title: Darbareye Elly
overview: The mysterious disappearance of a kindergarten teacher during a picnic in the north of Iran is followed by a series of misadventures for her fellow travelers.

title: Hiroshima mon amour
overview: A French actress filming an anti-war film in Hiroshima has an affair with a married Japanese architect as they share their differing perspectives on war.

title: Charade
overview: Romance and suspense ensue in Paris as a woman is pursued by several men who want a fortune her murdered husband had stolen. Whom can she trust?

title: Smultronstället
overview: After living a life marked by coldness, an aging professor is forced to confront the emptiness of his existence.

title: Hævnen
overview: The lives of two Danish families cross each other, and an extraordinary but risky friendship comes into bud. But loneliness, frailty and sorrow lie in wait.
